snippet.title: Smalland Gameplay Trailer - Future Games Show Gamescom 2021
snippet.description: Check out some big gameplay on a tiny scale from the multiplayer survival sim Smalland, learn to craft, build and fend off the creepy crawlies in a harsh environment. Smalland is coming soon to PC with a demo coming in October!
